        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2017-07-04 23:16:26.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nRather than waiting some arbitrary time, wouldn't it be better to do some sort of coordination between the processes (e.g. MPI_Barrier()) so that the test can run as fast as possible, and doesn't still have a chance to hang if one node is slow for some reason?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
