      "date": "2017-07-05 02:25:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review+1\n\nI agree with Andreas that this patch just reduces the deadlock possibility as temporary solution, not a perfect one.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
